<br>
The happiness is very contagious as even though I have been depressed  a bit for the week long tree form I have had to take, I find myself smiling. Someone asked me what happiness was to a blind person. It isnt what you see but what you feel from other people.<br>
<br>
I promise myself as soon as I get out of treeform, I will plan on making eviah and wardenn a very special gift. After all who can say no to edible goo and bog juice??!!<br>
<br>
Jelineth<br>
